weapon : Bat and gun board
power : 3/5

story :
After the black wave came and aroused the inner evil in every human being, the human who was still awake took refuge and hid himself. A skater uses his skateboard as a means of traveling and arming himself. In addition to distributing food supplies to humans for shelter, the Skaterbot is able to defeat the forces of evil with his tricks and weapons.
